other. License revenues are derived from the licensing of software products
while development fees are derived from development contracts that we have
entered into with other companies, including customers and development partners.
Maintenance and other recurring revenues are derived from maintenance fees
charged in the initial licensing year, renewals of annual maintenance services
in subsequent years and recurring


