         Net revenues were $159.4 million, $170.2 million and $134.9 million in
2002, 2001, and 2000, respectively, representing a decrease of 6% from 2001 to
2002 and an increase of 26% from 2000 to 2001. The decrease in net revenues from
2001 to 2002 primarily resulted in a decline in license and development fees
offset in part by an increase in maintenance and other recurring revenues. The
target clients for our products include a range of financial services
organizations that manage investment portfolios, including investment advisors,
brokerage firms, banks and hedge funds. In addition, we target corporations,
