proposed regulatory activity in the financial services market. These factors
have resulted in reduced revenue growth across the industry, longer sales
cycles, deferral and delay of information technology projects and generally
reduced expenditure for software related services. We expect a continued
difficult environment for the near term. The increase in license revenue from
2000 to 2001, in absolute dollars, was primarily due to increased demand for the
Advent Office suite to both new customers as well as follow-on sales to existing
customers, and for our Geneva software which is licensed primarily to global
financial institutions and hedge funds.

