     In February 2002, we acquired Kinexus Corporation, a privately held company
located in New York. The total purchase price of approximately $45.5 million
included cash of approximately $34 million, closing costs of $3 million and a
warrant to purchase 165,176 shares of our Common Stock valued at $8.5 million.
